  "subject": "Improve robot image building",
  "commit_message": "Improve robot image building\n\nCreating helper script to build robot (onap/testsuite)\nimage directly from git repo.\n\nCurrently robot image building steps are hidden in\nJenkins job and it's confusing from user perspective\nto know the content of image as not all code is in git.\n\nCreate build_docker.sh script that can be used also from\nJenkins to build the Robot image.\n\nIssue-ID: INT-1369\n\nSigned-off-by: Samuli Silvius <s.silvius@partner.samsung.com>\nChange-Id: Ide057f75c6eb304ed6e951f54ab2d3b57ea8a7d2\n",
